## Next Steps
To enable Speed Insights in production:
1. Deploy this change to Vercel
2. Navigate to the Speed Insights section in the Vercel dashboard
3. Click the "Enable" button to activate tracking
4. Verify the tracking script appears in the deployed page's head tag

## Notes
- The SpeedInsights component is lightweight and will not impact page performance
- Data collection is automatic once enabled in the Vercel dashboard
- Works alongside the existing Vercel Analytics setup without any conflicts
